 **** Files **** 

3 Ways to Read File

1. File Reader :-
	 Character by character
	 characterStream
	 returns -1 when done checking
	 
2.BufferReader :-
	reads by buffering
	return when !=null

3. Scanner
	reads line by line
	returns when there's no next line sc.hasNextLine()
	
